               <p>
                  <hi rend="smallCaps">
                     <persName id="t18421024-name-455" type="witnessName">
                        <interp inst="t18421024-name-455" type="gender" value="male"></interp>
                        <interp inst="t18421024-name-455" type="surname" value="BURTON"></interp>
                        <interp inst="t18421024-name-455" type="given" value="WILLIAM"></interp>WILLIAM BURTON</persName>
                  </hi>. I live in Henry-street, Pentonville. About half-past eleven o'clock on the 19th of October I was in Fleet-street—I felt, and my handkerchief was gone—a person behind me said the prisoner, who was going across the road, had taken it from me—I went and charged him with it—he said he had not got it—on turning round I found it be<lb></lb>hind me—this is it.</p>
               <p>
                  <hi rend="smallCaps">
